		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />the only feature i would add to asm6 is a chr and prg  label with a command line argument that makes it output the chr and prg files without changing anything <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
<br />
<br />;header stuff
<br />
<br />.prg
<br />;prg stuff here
<br />
<br />.chr
<br />;chr stuff here
<br />
<br />so for a .nes file you would assemble it with "asm6 main.asm rom.nes"
<br />and if you want it in two files something like "asm6 split main.asm rom.nes"
<br />output would be "rom.nes.prg" "rom.nes.chr"
<br />
<br />even thats pointless tho.. you could have main.asm then prg.asm and chr.asm

		

